 created backend and frontend folder differently.
 created Server.js (express Server).
 installed everything (tailwind, mongodb, bcrypt, react etc).
 created Database models.
 setup .env.
 created utils folder and created db.js file to connect db. 
 created controlers file for user control.
 created middlewares file to authenticate tokens.
 created dataUri in utils to convert image in URL.
 created cloudinary in utils and setup cloudinary.
 created multer.js file in middleware to upload profile picture.
 created user controls and post controls in controllers folder.
 created routes in routes folder for APIs.
 used 'thunder client' to test all the APIs.